pageTitle: Evergreen studios about to open their doors | CanyonCourier.com
TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {36353=Copyright © 2015, 29033=Canyon Courier | circulation@canyoncourier.com | 303-350-1030 27902 Meadow Drive, Ste 200, Evergreen, CO 80439 Office Hours are 8:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m., Monday through Friday, 23238=September is a time to celebrate the beauty of our mountain community. The first touches of gold appear on the aspen, and the hay meadows have changed from green to shades of copper. It is also a time to celebrate the artistic community in the greater Evergreen area by visiting the studios of our working artists. The 10th annual Open Door Studios of Evergreen offers a backstage look at the time, talent and techniques involved in the creation of the beautiful works of art that best capture the changing seasons of Evergreen and the world beyond.}
